<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6323060>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Two species of Krumbachia Reisinger, 1924. A–C. Krumbachia subterranea Reisinger, 1933. A. Internal organisation of a live specimen. B. Organisation of the genital system of a live specimen. C. Reconstruction of reproductive organs based on sagittal sections of the neotype (neotype no. 823). D–E. Krumbachia virginiana (Kepner & Carter, 1931) Ruebush, 1938. D. Internal organisation of a live specimen. E. Reconstruction of reproductive organs based on sagittal sections." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6323060/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

